{
  "stem": "26276.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It must have been something-- a new camp at that time-- that they just put up the barracks, and that was it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when the rain came or something, it was muddy, terribly muddy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And again, everybody had to throw their clothes off.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "While we were taking our clothes off, at that spot-- maybe about 30, 40 feet away-- there were a lot of barracks.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at the front of the barracks, there were a lot of piles of baby shoes, baby clothes, baby toys laying around.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we expected that they must have had here either a warehouse from other camps, that they shipped children's clothes-- that the children were killed already.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or they brought in children there and killed them in that camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the shoes with the clothes and everything else, they saved for their own children, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because at that time, it was too hard for them to find already clothes in the stores for them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that was the-- a terrible shock and a terrible sight to see those things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then after they checked us out, we had to march down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember it was a hill to march down from the place where we stayed to the barracks to get washed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "While we were doing this, we saw prisoners with huge pushcarts, like-- dead bodies on the pushcarts, going towards the crematorium to throw them in there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That went on like this every day, all day long-- back and forth, back and forth they would go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I-- that was in the mud.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you could see they struggled even to bring those wagons in or out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it went on like this every single day, every time whenever we went outside.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
